@startuml auth-flow
' Tchalanet — pipeline d'authentification et d'autorisation
' Avant tout appel de service (Controller → CommandBus)

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderThickness 1
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #888
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"

participant "Client\n(Web / POS)" as CLIENT
participant "Spring Security\nBearerTokenFilter" as SPRING #LightBlue
participant "TchAccess\nPipelineFilter" as PIPE #LightYellow
participant "TchContext\nFilter" as CTX #LightYellow
participant "Controller /\nCommandBus" as SVC #LightGreen
database "Firebase\n(JWT keys)" as FB #LightGray
database "Tchalanet DB" as DB #LightGray

== 1 · Toutes les requêtes : vérification JWT ==

CLIENT -> SPRING : Authorization: Bearer <firebase-jwt>\n[X-Tch-Client-Type: POS]  ← SELLER_TERMINAL uniquement
SPRING -> FB : vérifie signature + exp + iss
FB --> SPRING : ✓ JWT valide
SPRING -> SPRING : convert() → ExternalAuthenticatedUser\nstocké dans JwtAuthenticationToken.details\nautorities = []  (vide ici)

== 2 · PUBLIC  (/api/v1/public/**) ==

note over PIPE : shouldNotFilter = true\n→ PIPE entièrement skippé
CLIENT -> CTX : (pas de token requis)
CTX -> CTX : handlePublicOrLegacy()\ntenant public par défaut
CTX -> SVC : TchRequestContext\n· scope = PUBLIC\n· tenantId = default\n· actorType = null

== 3 · IDENTITY  (authentifié, scope public/identity) ==

SPRING -> PIPE
PIPE -> DB : findByFirebaseUid → app_user  (statut ACTIVE ?)
DB --> PIPE : ✓ app_user
PIPE -> PIPE : ResolvedAccessContext.identityOnly(userId)\n→ pas de rôles / permissions chargés
PIPE -> CTX
CTX -> CTX : handleResolvedAccess()
CTX -> SVC : TchRequestContext\n· scope = PUBLIC\n· actorType = APP_USER\n· appUserId = UUID\n· roleCodes = {}\n· permissionKeys = {}

== 4 · ADMIN / TENANT  (/api/v1/admin/** ou /tenant/**) ==

alt APP_USER  (X-Tch-Client-Type absent ou WEB)
    SPRING -> PIPE
    PIPE -> DB : findByFirebaseUid → app_user  (statut ACTIVE ?)
    DB --> PIPE : ✓ app_user
    PIPE -> DB : AccessControlSnapshotResolver\n· resolvePlatform(userId)\n· resolveTenant(userId, effectiveTenantId)
    DB --> PIPE : roleCodes + permissionKeys
    PIPE -> SPRING : enrichit JwtAuthenticationToken\n· ACTOR_APP_USER\n· ROLE_TENANT_ADMIN, …\n· PERM_seller_terminal.manage, …
    PIPE -> CTX
    CTX -> CTX : handleResolvedAccess()
    CTX -> DB : hydrateResolvedTenant()  (code / tz / currency)
    CTX -> CTX : bind RLS  ← PostgreSQL app.current_tenant activé
    CTX -> SVC : TchRequestContext\n· actorType = APP_USER\n· appUserId = UUID\n· roleCodes = {TENANT_ADMIN, …}\n· permissionKeys = {seller_terminal.manage, …}

else SELLER_TERMINAL  (X-Tch-Client-Type: POS)
    note over PIPE : Pas de fallback vers APP_USER !\n403 si firebase_uid introuvable\ndans seller_terminal
    SPRING -> PIPE
    PIPE -> DB : findByExternalIdentity(provider, issuer, firebase_uid)\n→ seller_terminal  (statut ACTIVE ?)
    DB --> PIPE : ✓ sellerTerminalId + tenantId
    PIPE -> PIPE : SELLER_TERMINAL_PERMISSIONS (hardcodées)\n· seller_terminal.me.read\n· seller_terminal.sell\n· seller_terminal.ticket.read_own\n· seller_terminal.ticket.reprint_own
    PIPE -> SPRING : enrichit JwtAuthenticationToken\n· ACTOR_SELLER_TERMINAL\n· PERM_seller_terminal.sell, …
    PIPE -> CTX
    CTX -> CTX : handleResolvedAccess()
    note over CTX : X-Tenant-Id / X-Tch-Tenant-Override\ninterdit → 403 si présents
    CTX -> DB : hydrateResolvedTenant()  (tenant from DB, jamais from header)
    CTX -> CTX : bind RLS
    CTX -> SVC : TchRequestContext\n· actorType = SELLER_TERMINAL\n· sellerTerminalId = UUID\n· roleCodes = {}\n· permissionKeys = {seller_terminal.sell, …}
end

== 5 · PLATFORM  (/api/v1/platform/**) ==

SPRING -> PIPE
PIPE -> DB : findByFirebaseUid → app_user
DB --> PIPE : ✓ app_user
PIPE -> DB : resolvePlatform(userId) uniquement\n(pas de tenant résolu)
DB --> PIPE : roleCodes platform + permissionKeys platform
PIPE -> SPRING : ACTOR_APP_USER + ROLE_SUPER_ADMIN + PERM_platform.*
PIPE -> CTX
CTX -> CTX : handleResolvedAccess()  (pas de tenant par défaut)
CTX -> SVC : TchRequestContext\n· scope = PLATFORM\n· actorType = APP_USER\n· superAdmin = true\n· tenantId = null

== 6 · Autorisation fine — toutes requêtes authentifiées ==

SVC -> SVC : @PreAuthorize("hasPermission(null, 'seller_terminal.manage')")\n→ TchPermissionEvaluator vérifie PERM_* dans JwtAuthenticationToken.authorities\n→ allow / deny

@enduml
